<!-- HERO -->
<section class="homehero-section text-white text-center d-flex align-items-center">
  <div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Optometrists Vanguard</h1>

    <p class="lead mx-auto mb-4 text-white-75" style="max-width:800px;">
      We are a community of Nigerian optometrists living and practicing in Saudi Arabia. 
      Our platform was created to make the journey of settling into the Kingdom easier, 
      friendlier, and more rewarding for fellow colleagues. Here you’ll find practical 
      advice, shared experiences, and resources to help you navigate both professional 
      and everyday life. From learning simple Arabic phrases for smoother communication, 
      to tips on adapting to local culture, we make sure no one feels alone in the process. 
      We also provide spaces to connect: a job board for new opportunities, and a small 
      marketplace where members can buy and sell equipment or household items — especially 
      useful when moving between cities within the Kingdom. At the heart of it all, this is 
      a family-friendly hub where older colleagues pass down wisdom, newer colleagues find 
      support, and together we grow into a stronger, thriving network of Nigerian optometrists 
      in Saudi Arabia.
    </p>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4">Log In</a>
      <a href="/add_new_user" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4">Register</a>
    </div>

    <div class="homehero-image mt-5">
      <img src="./images/opt.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-lg" width="720">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

